                  {
                    "text": "The Court recognizes the advantages of ADR in promoting efficiency, cost-effectiveness, and the preservation of relationships between the parties. Moreover, ADR can often lead to outcomes that are mutually satisfactory and tailored to the specific needs of the parties involved.",
